e the unfairness will be much higher due to time it takes to download a block.  Breaking the block into more and more atomic chunks means it can be approached [[https://lists.linuxfoundation.org/pipermail/bitcoin-dev/2015-September/011176.html|#]].  7s blocktime gives 0.9548276244%25 unfairness.  6s blocktime gives 1.1139655617%25 unfairness.
